<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h1>Thank you for booking a flight with us, <%= @passenger.name %></h1>
    <p>
      You have successfully booked your flight for <%= @passenger.booking.tickets %> person(s) from <%= @passenger.booking.flight.from_airport.code %>
      to <%= @passenger.booking.flight.to_airport.code %> on <%= @passenger.booking.flight.start_time.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %> 
      at <%= @passenger.booking.flight.start_time.strftime("%H:%M") %>.<br>
    </p>
    <p>
      To view your booking, visit: <%= @url %>.
    </p>
    <p>Thanks for booking with us and have a safe flight!</p>
  </body>
</html>